		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Thu, Jun 20th 2:26 AM 2002 </span><span id="notbold">| <span class=sm>IP: Logged</span> | <a class=sm href="/db/classes.html?class=1&mid=102455387372564&post=1&replyto=102455387372564"><img src=/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=11 width=17> Reply to this</a></a> | <a class=sm href="/db/journal2.html?user=124705">User's Journal</a>  <a name=102455387372564></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=124705"><span id=Scholar>Deckert</span></a><b><span id=Scholar><br>Scholar</span></b><br>31 posts
		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</nobr><br><br><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>Everfrost is an excellent place to make cash as a new player.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>Kill every bear you see, even after they cease to give experience.  HQ Bear skins sell well to tailors, and on my server go for anywhere from 25-40pp.  Also, learn to turn skins into leather padding (see EQTraders for how) which sells well.<br><br>Likewise, spider and spiderling silks sell great to tailors/blacksmiths.<br><br>Bone chips also sell well...up to 5pp per stack.  <br><br>All these items above stack, and I'd recommend banking them up for a few levels and trying to sell them in quantity.<br><br>Another reliable money maker in Everfrost is banking for players hunting Ice Giants.  This is my least favorite money maker, but it can yield some decent cash and some finesteel weaps from players who are encumbered with small coins and weapons.  Can be dangerous getting there and back to town at lower levels.<br><br>Final $$ idea in Everfrost is untested, but here goes... Ice Goblin Blood is used in some very very high skill level Barbarian blacksmithing recipes.  If you happen across any of those I'd hold onto them and try and trade them for some armor or whatnot. Dont know the rarity or demand for these, but might be worth a try.<br><br>Safe and profitable hunting to you.<br><br>Edit: just so im clear...when i say something sells well i mean sells to other players. never sell skins, silks, bonechips to vendors.  They wont give you near what other players will.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Thu Jun 20 02:22:28 2002</em></p><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Frostpaw<br>65 Barbarian Warrior<br>Cazic Thule Server</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replie